<view class="page-shell index-shell">
  <view class="hero">
    <view class="hero-badge">
      <view class="hero-badge-dot"></view>
      <text>聚会桌游 · 小程序版</text>
    </view>
    <view class="hero-title">
      <text class="hero-title-main">谁是卧底</text>
      <text class="hero-title-accent">Find the Undercover</text>
    </view>
    <view class="hero-sub">找出那个说着不一样词的人。</view>

    <view class="hero-illu">
      <view class="hero-card hero-card-a">
        <view class="hero-card-word">苹果</view>
        <view class="hero-card-pinyin">píng guǒ</view>
      </view>
      <view class="hero-card hero-card-b">
        <view class="hero-card-word">？？</view>
        <view class="hero-card-pinyin hero-card-pinyin-mute">who knows</view>
      </view>
      <view class="hero-card hero-card-c">
        <view class="hero-card-word">梨</view>
        <view class="hero-card-pinyin">lí</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <setup-panel
    player-count-options="{{playerCountOptions}}"
    selected-player-count="{{playerCount}}"
    categories="{{categories}}"
    selected-category-id="{{categoryId}}"
    can-start="{{canStart}}"
    bind:selectcount="onSelectCount"
    bind:selectcategory="onSelectCategory"
    bind:startgame="onStartGame"
  />

  <view class="tips-card">
    <view class="tips-title">
      <text class="tips-bullet">玩</text>
      <text>玩法提示</text>
    </view>
    <view class="tips-list">
      <view class="tips-item">
        <text class="tips-index">1</text>
        <text class="tips-text">设置人数与词库，系统会随机挑出一名卧底。</text>
      </view>
      <view class="tips-item">
        <text class="tips-index">2</text>
        <text class="tips-text">玩家依次点击卡片查看自己的词，大多数人相同，只有卧底不同。</text>
      </view>
      <view class="tips-item">
        <text class="tips-index">3</text>
        <text class="tips-text">线下轮流描述词语，票选出最可疑的人，最后揭晓真相。</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
